Package address

Class AddressBook

java.lang.Object
address.AddressBook
public class AddressBook
extends java.lang.Object
Holds a collection of objects of the class AddressEntry Contains an add method to add new AddressEntry Contains an list method to iterate through an ArrayList of AddressEntry
